messages.message:
Heads up if anyone is seeing `aihub-derived-field` or `aihub-custom-function` cypress CI tests failing because the test can’t find the right field type in the dropdown, its most likely because your frontend code is out of date example cypress run (https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/18638/overview/5b99dc40-cd03-49a8-9db0-6919eb01f86b/replay?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1&ts=1743119334792.7998&att=1)

Serena recently merged a PR to remove the derived field and custom function flags, so you’ll need to merge master or else the frontend will still try to look for those flags. (Can also delete/recreate sandbox but I think merging master should be enough!)
oh oops :sweat_smile: thanks for catching and announcing! :raised_hands:
